snippet.title: Sonic XG Development Material - Final Fall Zone, Act 1 (2021 version)
snippet.description:
Over the past year, we have spent a lot of time making sure the level design is better fitted for XG's character moveset. This instance shows the earliest version of the new iteration of Final Fall act 1 from April 2021.

Note that what's currently shown in this footage is not up-to-date with current versions of the game, everything is still subject to change!

If you haven't already, please follow our Twitter page for future updates and trivia! 
https://twitter.com/Sonic_XG
